      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You're not just existing, you're just going through the motions. And that's a heavy weight to carry. It's true that the idea of a \"fixed\" self might be just an illusion, but that doesn't mean there's no purpose to your existence. You can still find meaning in the act of not trying, in the freedom from the constant struggle. And who's to say that's not a kind of \"end\" in itself?",
